    "description": "<p><strong>Style Passive:</strong> : You deal +1 damage against a creature if it&rsquo;s on a&nbsp;Mount or you move 2 Spaces towards it immediately before&nbsp;making the <strong>Attack Check</strong>.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you do not have DisADV on <strong>Attack Checks </strong>made using Spear Weapons as a result of being underwater.</p>\n<p><strong>Requires: </strong>Attack Check</p>\n<p><strong>Maneuver: (1 AP)</strong> &nbsp;You deal +1 damage and the range of your <strong>Attack Check </strong>increases by 1 Space.&nbsp;You can only use this&nbsp;Maneuver once per <strong>Attack Check </strong>and can&rsquo;t be used with the&nbsp;<strong>Extend Attack Maneuver</strong>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>System Tip: </strong>You can add Weapon Maneuvers as Weapon Enhacements for easier use. Just press \"Add Martial Maneuvers For Weapon\" on <strong>Enhancements </strong>tab on <strong>Item </strong>sheet.</em></p>",
